---
name: "写作设置"
type: prompt_component
category: components
inputs:
  - name: tense
    label: Tense
    description: Narrative tense for the output
    custom_content: true
    options:
      - "past"
      - "present"
  - name: pov
    label: Point of View
    description: Narrative perspective
    custom_content: true
    options:
      - "1st"
      - "2nd"
      - "3rd"
      - "3rd-limited"
      - "3rd-omniscient"
  - name: language
    label: Language
    description: Output language
    custom_content: true
    options:
      - "zh-CN"
      - "en"
      - "zh-TW"
      - "ja"
      - "ko"
---
{% if tense is defined and tense == "present" %}
写作要求：使用现在时叙述。
{% elif tense is defined and tense == "past" %}
写作要求：使用过去时叙述。
{% endif %}
{% if pov is defined %}
叙述视角：{% if pov == "1st" %}第一人称{% elif pov == "2nd" %}第二人称{% elif pov == "3rd" %}第三人称{% elif pov == "3rd-limited" %}第三人称有限视角{% elif pov == "3rd-omniscient" %}第三人称全知视角{% endif %}。
{% endif %}
{% if language is defined and language != "zh-CN" %}

写作语言：{% if language == "en" %}英语{% elif language == "zh-TW" %}繁體中文{% elif language == "ja" %}日本語{% elif language == "ko" %}한국어{% else %}{{ language }}{% endif %}。
{% endif %}
{% if narrative_character is defined and narrative_character %}

叙事视角角色（请以该角色的视角和口吻进行叙述）：
{{ narrative_character }}
{% endif %}
